免责声明 / Disclaimer
================================================================================

本项目数据来源于公开渠道整理,仅供参考。期刊收录情况、刊期信息、收稿
要求等可能随时变化,实际投稿请以期刊官方公告为准。作者不对因使用本工
具产生的任何投稿决策后果承担责任。

The journal data is compiled from publicly available sources and is for
reference only. Journal indexing, publication frequency, and submission
requirements may change. Authors should verify with official journal
announcements before submitting. The compiler assumes no responsibility
for any consequences arising from the use of this tool.

